<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/633036-not-exactly-about-this-book-but-i-was">Not exactly about this book, but I was wondering if other introverts have trouble calling up ingredients l immediate family members or close friends even once in a while? Like, I can stand talking on the phone but I almost never initiate it.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_633036'><a id="like_count_community_question_633036" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/633036?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">60 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F8520610-quiet">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/633036-not-exactly-about-this-book-but-i-was">6 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/633036-not-exactly-about-this-book-but-i-was">See all 20 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

